&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is at the front line of VTS’s growth engine. In this expanded version of a traditional SDR role, you’re cultivating relationships and ensuring long-term customer value. You will help identify and engage users of our Activate platform with the aim to increase their adoption of our product. Leveraging data-driven workflows and senior leadership strategies, you’ll generate pipeline at scale, test new go-to-market strategies, and provide critical insights back to the sales and marketing teams.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
