&lt;p&gt;This role sits at the intersection of sales, solution design, and implementation readiness. Once an opportunity is qualified, the Solutions Consultant becomes the solutions expert alongside the Account Executive - translating a customer’s needs into a tailored Activate solution and, once the deal is won, into a complete solution design and implementation plan that hands off cleanly to the Implementation team. You will work predominantly through our major channel partners to start, expanding to the direct channel and other commercial clients over time, and partner closely with our Senior Technical Solutions Consultant, whose deep access-control expertise verifies and completes the solution you design.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unlike a traditional pre-sales engineer focused only on the demonstration, or an implementation manager focused only on delivery, this position helps manage the full arc of solution implementation preparedness - from qualified opportunity, through solution design, to a clean handoff to implementation, with continued check-ins through launch. It carries deep product ownership of the Activate feature set, with particular emphasis on Access Control and Visitor Management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a highly visible, senior individual-contributor role based in our New York office.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;** Please note that this opportunity requires this hire to work from our NYC office four days a week. **&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
