&lt;li&gt;Aggregate everything learned during the sale into a single solution design - requirements, the technologies and features being deployed, and the rollout schedule - documented in the deal journal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce a complete, unambiguous handoff package so the Implementation team can execute without rework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Senior Technical Solutions Consultant to verify and complete the solution - integrations, APIs, custom development, and access-control specifics&lt;/li&gt;
